00:18:13,406 --> 00:18:16,656
So, I have to call
startOfDateForDay--


321
00:18:17,356 --> 00:18:21,336
startOfDayForDate,
excuse me, again once more


322
00:18:21,876 --> 00:18:25,216
to compute the real
