00:33:46,256 --> 00:33:48,806
in an NSDateComponents
simply have a value


587
00:33:48,836 --> 00:33:50,876
of NSDateComponents
and specified.


588
00:33:51,776 --> 00:33:53,736
Well, that doesn't tell
us what the algorithm does


