00:39:03,156 --> 00:39:04,376
in the Gregorian calendar.


677
00:39:04,376 --> 00:39:06,416
You want to find the
next February 29th.


678
00:39:07,126 --> 00:39:10,116
Well, that could be as much
as four years in the future.


